  <div class="program-description-content bottom-left">
    <p>The Department of Toxic Substances Control (DTSC) wants your comments about a proposed cleanup plan at the former Ramona Elementary School. The former school site is at 1524 West 7th Street, San Bernardino, CA 92411.</p>

