      </span>
      <span><strong>The cleanup would contain and remove lead-based paint in debris from the site.</strong></span>
    </p>

    <p>DTSC proposes:</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Burying contaminated debris and soil</li>
    <li>Removing contaminated soil from the site</li>
    <li>Covering backfill with asphalt or concrete</li>
    <li>Restricting what can be built on this site after cleanup</li>
    </ul>
